    (2, 4, 'Catching Bees With Honey, Not Vinegar', 'Kindness and empathy are some of the most powerful tools at your disposal', 'https://techcrunch.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/IMG_0729-2.jpg', '{"Kindness and Empathy Are Some of the Most Powerful Tools at Your Disposal", "Givers can get more than takers", "Being kind elicits kindness", "Understanding their side can foster a closer connection", "Being loved is better than being feared", "Always err on the side of kindness"}', FALSE),
